nodes.text: Tamwith Bay was a city on the planet Raxus Secundus, located some distance from the planetary capital of Raxulon. While on an undercover mission to assassinate Count Dooku, head of the Confederacy of Independent Systems, Quinlan Vos and Asajj Ventress travelled to Tamwith Bay to purchase suitable clothing for the Raxian Humanitarian Award gala.
